snippet.title: Maiden Cops final Trailer is here!
snippet.description:
Our new game is almost here! On September 23rd we'll release our new game, #maidencops on #STEAM!

#wishlist now, and don't miss the release!

And if you know a streamer/content creator that you they'll know will like our game, tag them in the comments below!
